{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":793,"text":"I want to give you a new perspective."},{"time":4000,"text":"That sounds grandiose, and it is."},{"time":7560,"text":"I left Ireland yesterday morning."},{"time":9880,"text":"I traveled from Dublin to New York"},{"time":12360,"text":"independently."},{"time":14080,"text":"But the design of an airport,"},{"time":16000,"text":"plane and terminal"},{"time":18560,"text":"offers little independence when\nyou're 105 and a half centimeters tall."},{"time":23200,"text":"For Americans, that's 3' 5\"."},{"time":27680,"text":"I was whisked through the airport\nby airline assistants in a wheelchair."},{"time":32000,"text":"Now, I don't need to use a wheelchair,"},{"time":35680,"text":"but the design of an airport"},{"time":37800,"text":"and its lack of accessibility"},{"time":40080,"text":"means that it's my only way\nto get through."},{"time":43280,"text":"With my carry-on bag between my feet,"},{"time":46040,"text":"I was wheeled through\nsecurity, preclearance"},{"time":49440,"text":"and I arrived at my boarding gate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52880,"text":"I use the accessibility\nservices in the airport"},{"time":55760,"text":"because most of the terminal\nis just not designed with me in mind."},{"time":59920,"text":"Take security, for example."},{"time":62320,"text":"I'm not strong enough\nto lift my carry-on bag"},{"time":65440,"text":"from the ground to the carousel."},{"time":68480,"text":"I stand at eye level with it."},{"time":70560,"text":"And those who work in that space\nfor safety purposes cannot help me"},{"time":75520,"text":"and cannot do it for me."},{"time":78200,"text":"Design inhibits my autonomy\nand my independence."},{"time":83000,"text":"But traveling at this size,\nit isn't all bad."},{"time":86960,"text":"The leg room in economy\nis like business class."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":92760,"text":"I often forget that I'm a little person."},{"time":95360,"text":"It's the physical environment\nand society that remind me."},{"time":100120,"text":"Using a public bathroom\nis an excruciating experience."},{"time":104880,"text":"I walk into the cubicle"},{"time":107080,"text":"but I can't reach the lock on the door."},{"time":109880,"text":"I'm creative and resilient."},{"time":113000,"text":"I look around and see if there's\na bin that I can turn upside down."},{"time":117400,"text":"Is it safe?"},{"time":119040,"text":"Not really."},{"time":120640,"text":"Is it hygienic and sanitary?"},{"time":123440,"text":"Definitely not."},{"time":125760,"text":"But the alternative is much worse."},{"time":128240,"text":"If that doesn't work, I use my phone."},{"time":131160,"text":"It gives me an additional\nfour- to six-inch reach,"},{"time":134240,"text":"and I try to jam the lock closed\nwith my iPhone."},{"time":137720,"text":"Now, I imagine that's not what Jony Ive\nhad in mind when he designed the iPhone,"},{"time":142160,"text":"but it works."},{"time":144960,"text":"The alternative\nis that I approach a stranger."},{"time":148480,"text":"I apologize profusely"},{"time":150760,"text":"and I ask them to stand guard\noutside my cubicle door."},{"time":155000,"text":"They do"},{"time":156560,"text":"and I emerge grateful"},{"time":159480,"text":"but absolutely mortified,"},{"time":162040,"text":"and hope that they didn't notice"},{"time":163800,"text":"that I left the bathroom\nwithout washing my hands."},{"time":167200,"text":"I carry hand sanitizer with me\nevery single day"},{"time":171240,"text":"because the sink, soap dispenser,\nhand dryer and mirror"},{"time":176600,"text":"are all out of my reach."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179120,"text":"Now, the accessible bathroom\nis somewhat of an option."},{"time":181880,"text":"In this space, I can reach\nthe lock on the door,"},{"time":184840,"text":"the sink, the soap dispenser,\nthe hand dryer and the mirror."},{"time":190400,"text":"Yet, I cannot use the toilet."},{"time":194520,"text":"It is deliberately designed higher"},{"time":197000,"text":"so that wheelchair users\ncan transfer across with ease."},{"time":201200,"text":"This is a wonderful\nand necessary innovation,"},{"time":205440,"text":"but in the design world, when we describe\na new project or idea as accessible,"},{"time":210680,"text":"what does that mean?"},{"time":212920,"text":"Who is it accessible to?"},{"time":215840,"text":"And whose needs\nare not being accommodated for?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"Now, the bathroom is an example"},{"time":221520,"text":"of where design impinges upon my dignity,"},{"time":224920,"text":"but the physical environment impacts\nupon me in much more casual ways too,"},{"time":229240,"text":"something as simple\nas ordering a cup of coffee."},{"time":232320,"text":"Now, I'll admit it."},{"time":234160,"text":"I drink far too much coffee."},{"time":236480,"text":"My order is a skinny vanilla latte,"},{"time":239080,"text":"but I'm trying\nto wean myself off the syrup."},{"time":242800,"text":"But the coffee shop,\nit's not designed well,"},{"time":245560,"text":"at least not for me."},{"time":247520,"text":"Queuing, I'm standing\nbeside the pastry cabinet"},{"time":250320,"text":"and the barista calls for the next order."},{"time":253200,"text":"\"Next, please!\" they shout."},{"time":256440,"text":"They can't see me."},{"time":258640,"text":"The person next to me in the queue\npoints to my existence"},{"time":261480,"text":"and everyone is embarrassed."},{"time":264240,"text":"I order as quick as I can\nand I move along to collect my coffee."},{"time":268480,"text":"Now, think just for a second."},{"time":271560,"text":"Where do they put it?"},{"time":273960,"text":"Up high and without a lid."},{"time":276480,"text":"Reaching up to collect a coffee\nthat I have paid for"},{"time":279400,"text":"is an incredibly dangerous experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282640,"text":"But design also impinges\non the clothes that I want to wear."},{"time":285920,"text":"I want garments\nthat reflect my personality."},{"time":289320,"text":"It's difficult to find\nin the childrenswear department."},{"time":292640,"text":"And often womenswear\nrequires far too many alterations."},{"time":296600,"text":"I want shoes that affect my maturity,\nprofessionalism and sophistication."},{"time":302160,"text":"Instead, I'm offered sneakers\nwith Velcro straps and light-up shoes."},{"time":307200,"text":"Now, I'm not totally opposed\nto light-up shoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":313080,"text":"But design also impacts\non such simple things,"},{"time":316520,"text":"like sitting on a chair."},{"time":318920,"text":"I cannot go from a standing\nto a seating position with grace."},{"time":323320,"text":"Due to the standards\nof design heights of chairs,"},{"time":326600,"text":"I have to crawl on my hands and knees"},{"time":329320,"text":"just to get on top of it,"},{"time":330960,"text":"whilst also being conscious\nthat it might tip over at any stage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336120,"text":"But whilst design impacts on me"},{"time":337960,"text":"whether it's a chair,\na bathroom, a coffee shop, or clothes,"},{"time":342760,"text":"I rely on and benefit"},{"time":345960,"text":"from the kindness of strangers."},{"time":349520,"text":"But not everybody is so nice."},{"time":352400,"text":"I'm reminded that I'm a little person"},{"time":355000,"text":"when a stranger points,"},{"time":357520,"text":"stares,"},{"time":359320,"text":"laughs,"},{"time":361360,"text":"calls me a name,"},{"time":363160,"text":"or takes a photograph of me."},{"time":365960,"text":"This happens almost every day."},{"time":368720,"text":"With the rise of social media,\nit has given me an opportunity"},{"time":371640,"text":"and a platform to have a voice\nas a blogger and as an activist,"},{"time":376440,"text":"but it has also made me nervous"},{"time":378760,"text":"that I might become a meme"},{"time":380880,"text":"or a viral sensation,"},{"time":383400,"text":"all without my consent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386240,"text":"So let's take a moment right now"},{"time":388960,"text":"to make something very clear."},{"time":391720,"text":"The word \"midget\" is a slur."},{"time":395360,"text":"It evolved from PT Barnum's era\nof circuses and freak shows."},{"time":400640,"text":"Society has evolved."},{"time":403520,"text":"So should our vocabulary."},{"time":405840,"text":"Language is a powerful tool."},{"time":408240,"text":"It does not just name our society."},{"time":410720,"text":"It shapes it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412880,"text":"I am incredibly proud\nto be a little person,"},{"time":416320,"text":"to have inherited\nthe condition of achondroplasia."},{"time":419600,"text":"But I am most proud to be Sinead."},{"time":422680,"text":"Achondroplasia is\nthe most common form of dwarfism."},{"time":426400,"text":"Achondroplasia translates\nas \"without cartilage formation.\""},{"time":430760,"text":"I have short limbs\nand achondroplastic facial features,"},{"time":434520,"text":"my forehead and my nose."},{"time":437560,"text":"My arms do not straighten fully,"},{"time":440200,"text":"but I can lick my elbow."},{"time":442640,"text":"I'm not showing you that one."},{"time":445200,"text":"Achondroplasia occurs in approximately\none in every 20,000 births."},{"time":450520,"text":"80 percent of little people\nare born to two average-height parents."},{"time":455000,"text":"That means that anybody in this room\ncould have a child with achondroplasia."},{"time":459960,"text":"Yet, I inherited my condition from my dad."},{"time":463880,"text":"I'd like to show you a photo of my family."},{"time":467280,"text":"My mother is average height,"},{"time":469320,"text":"my father is a little person"},{"time":471560,"text":"and I am the eldest of five children."},{"time":474200,"text":"I have three sisters and one brother."},{"time":477560,"text":"They are all average height."},{"time":480160,"text":"I am incredibly fortunate\nto have been born into a family"},{"time":483600,"text":"that cultivated\nmy curiosity and my tenacity,"},{"time":487720,"text":"that protected me from the unkindness\nand ignorance of strangers"},{"time":492720,"text":"and that armed me with the resilience,\ncreativity and confidence"},{"time":496920,"text":"that I needed to survive and manipulate\nthe physical environment and society."},{"time":502800,"text":"If I was to pinpoint any reason\nwhy I am successful,"},{"time":506640,"text":"it is because I was\nand I am a loved child,"},{"time":511560,"text":"now, a loved child\nwith a lot of sass and sarcasm,"},{"time":515480,"text":"but a loved child nonetheless."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518360,"text":"In giving you an insight\ninto who I am today"},{"time":522280,"text":"I wanted to offer you a new perspective."},{"time":525200,"text":"I wanted to challenge the idea"},{"time":526680,"text":"that design is but a tool\nto create function and beauty."},{"time":531280,"text":"Design greatly impacts\nupon people's lives,"},{"time":535400,"text":"all lives."},{"time":537360,"text":"Design is a way in which\nwe can feel included in the world,"},{"time":541080,"text":"but it is also a way in which\nwe can uphold a person's dignity"},{"time":545360,"text":"and their human rights."},{"time":547600,"text":"Design can also inflict vulnerability"},{"time":550320,"text":"on a group whose needs aren't considered."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554320,"text":"So today, I want\nyour perceptions challenged."},{"time":558880,"text":"Who are we not designing for?"},{"time":561000,"text":"How can we amplify their voices"},{"time":563840,"text":"and their experiences?"},{"time":566200,"text":"What is the next step?"},{"time":568400,"text":"Design is an enormous privilege,"},{"time":571000,"text":"but it is a bigger responsibility."},{"time":573960,"text":"I want you to open your eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576760,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}